Configure data source for Linux

1. 	
Start a terminal.
2. 	
As superuser, navigate to the Edge System installation directory: /opt/EdgeSystem.
3. 	
To configure a data source, run this command:

./OSIsoft.Data.System.Host Configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSource IpAddress=IpAddress Port=TcpPort

4. 	
Optional: To view configured data sources, run this command:

./OSIsoft.Data.System.Host Configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSource
